proposing to do to Gilfoyle.

19:24.758 --> 19:27.259
We're talking about
criminal charges here.

19:27.259 --> 19:28.842
He could be deported.

19:28.842 --> 19:30.676
There has to be
another option.

19:30.676 --> 19:32.676
Well, no offense, Jared,

19:32.676 --> 19:34.842
but Ben says there isn't.

19:34.842 --> 19:37.092
Okay? And he is
a world-class COO

19:37.092 --> 19:39.967
that has brought
multiple companies
to a billion dollars.

19:39.967 --> 19:41.967
And you're just
a biz dev guy.

19:41.967 --> 19:44.050
♪ ♪

19:44.050 --> 19:46.842
I'm-- I'm sorry. I--

19:46.842 --> 19:49.842
I just think that
in this particular situation,

19:49.842 --> 19:52.467
Ben might know
a little better.

19:54.175 --> 19:56.050
Okay.

19:56.050 --> 19:57.467
You're the boss.

20:00.509 --> 20:01.925
You know,
but I will say this.

20:01.925 --> 20:04.800
If you're really going
to start working with Ben,

20:04.800 --> 20:06.634
at least give Dana
the common courtesy

20:06.634 --> 20:08.842
of telling him the truth
about what you guys are doing.

20:09.800 --> 20:12.592
