21:03.092 --> 21:04.551
Jian

21:05.717 --> 21:09.175
So... Ben told me everything.

21:09.175 --> 21:11.050
Oh!

21:11.050 --> 21:12.883
Uh...

21:12.883 --> 21:14.134
Well...

21:14.134 --> 21:15.842
Radical candor,
I guess, right?

21:15.842 --> 21:18.342
Yeah, he told me how
you kept texting him non-stop.

21:18.342 --> 21:21.384
