22:16.967 --> 22:20.050
You and me, huh, Richard?

22:20.050 --> 22:21.175
Together, at last.

22:21.175 --> 22:22.758
Yeah.

22:24.634 --> 22:26.467
Dana rides a motorcycle?

22:26.467 --> 22:27.676
