23:08.676 --> 23:11.008
I checked their firmware
and their logs.

23:11.008 --> 23:13.592
The fridge is set
to record constantly

23:13.592 --> 23:14.967
streaming everything
back to the cloud.

23:14.967 --> 23:16.883
