23:25.634 --> 23:27.509
Shit.

23:27.509 --> 23:29.175
They make smoke detectors.

23:29.175 --> 23:30.842
I think there's one
in the kitchen.

23:30.842 --> 23:32.467
Those fuckers are listening.

23:34.175 --> 23:35.551
